text.paragraph:
When taken with Doxepin HCl Tablets, the sedative effects of alcoholic beverages, sedating antihistamines, and other CNS depressants may be potentiated [see Warnings and Precautions (5.2) and  Drug Interactions (7.3, 7.4)
                           ]. Patients should not consume alcohol with Doxepin HCl Tablets [see Warnings and Precautions (5.2) and  Drug Interactions (7.3)
                           ]. Patients should be cautioned about potential additive effects of Doxepin HCl Tablets used in combination with CNS depressants or sedating antihistamines [see Warnings and Precautions (5.2) and Drug Interactions (7.4)
                           ].
